name: Rocking New Year JACKPOT Event Poster
description:
This NFT was created to giveaway during the event and all leftovers will be burned when the event ends.  We will originally mint 2022 in celebration of the new year and this will be the only NFT in the event with editions of more than 22.  One edition will be included in the JACKPOT PRIZE!

All Hic Et Nunc artist are invited to participate.  

Please go to Twitter at https://twitter.com/rblbab/status/1469650566439931906 to find out more information about the event and how to join in and contact any host with any questions.  

Hosted by @rblbab @TerosEso @brainksy @ninacrypto2 and @Erythric.  Tech and tool by @NFTbiker

The jackpot for this event will be awarded to one COLLECTOR of any primary edition event token through a series of online spin drawings.  (see above link)

Royalties from secondary sales will go to help with expenses of this or future HEN community events or HEN community based charity efforts.
